t how do they expect us to put any of these things to use if we cannot get a group to use them in? I know I should be used to this now seeing as I'm 61. But, I don't think anyone can really ever get used to not being wanted. Very disheartening. <p><center><FONT SIZE=1><img src="http://212.212.159.196/yomad/imagesP/sorarn.gif"><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=411571">[ Magelo ]</a><br><i><b>Arch Mage of Luclin</i></b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=turzem>Turzem</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 97<br> <font color=#333333>(11/16/02 8:49:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7880.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~yolora/personal.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mages...a dying class?</span><hr size=1> I sometimes have problems, but if I REALLY want a group I will always get one. Just zone into PoK, do a / lfg, send a tell to a healer, and then a melee, and zone in somewhere. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:perpetua;font-size:x-small;"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=421973">Turzem Setanta</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->--<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower">Arch Mage</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kalahadbb>KalahadBB</A></span><br> <spa